OL,3,CSummerland 50th Anniversary: What
OL,4,Chappened and why does it matter?
OL,6,FThe Summerland disaster is the Isle of
OL,7,FMan's greatest tragedy.
OL,9,FA total of 50 people died, and 80 more
OL,10,Fwere seriously injured, after a fire
OL,11,Fspread through the island's leisure
OL,12,Fcomplex on 2 August 1973.
OL,14,FIt was, at the time, the worst
OL,15,Fpeacetime loss of life in a fire
OL,16,Fdisaster since the blitz, and many who
OL,17,Fsuffered feel the catastrophe has
OL,18,Fnever been truly recognised.
