OL,3,CSummerland 50th Anniversary: What
OL,4,Chappened and why does it matter?
OL,6,FThe blaze has been widely recognised
OL,7,Fas one which, had lessons been learnt
OL,8,Ffrom, could have foretold the Grenfell
OL,9,Fdisaster.
OL,11,FOf the 50 who tragically died, 11 of
OL,12,Fthem were under the age of twenty.
OL,14,FHow did the fire start?
OL,16,FThe fire was sparked by three young
OL,17,Fboys from Liverpool who were smoking
OL,18,Fin a small disused kiosk at around
OL,19,F7.30pm on 2 August 1973.
