OL,3,CSummerland 50th Anniversary: What
OL,4,Chappened and why does it matter?
OL,6,FA discarded cigarette caused the kiosk
OL,7,Fto catch fire, which then collapsed
OL,8,Fagainst the building, and within
OL,9,Fminutes it was ablaze.
OL,11,FFlames then spread undetected up the
OL,12,Finside of flammable cladding called
OL,13,FGalbestos.
OL,15,FRemarkably, during this time there was
OL,16,Fno attempt to evacuate the 3,000
OL,17,Fpeople inside.
OL,19,FThis was until visible flames appeared
OL,20,Fthrough a vent, causing a rushed panic
OL,21,Ftowards the doors.
