OL,6,FOnce the fire brigade had arrived, the
OL,7,Fwhole building was ablaze.
OL,9,F50 people were killed and over 80 were
OL,10,Finjured.
OL,12,FThe Inquiry
OL,14,FA public inquiry titled 'The
OL,15,FSummerland Fire Commission' (SFC) was
OL,16,Fpublished in May 1974.
