OL,3,CSummerland 50th Anniversary: What
OL,4,Chappened and why does it matter?
OL,6,FIt found the primary cause of the
OL,7,Fdisaster was due to the use of non
OL,8,Ffire-resistant materials, including
OL,9,FGalbestos, being used on the external
OL,10,Fwall.
OL,12,FFlames spread up a 12-inch gap between
OL,13,Fthe external wall and the internal
OL,14,Fcombustible fibreboard wall which
OL,15,Fcaused the flames to build in
OL,16,Fintensity.
OL,18,FThe fire then continued up to the roof
OL,19,Fcausing the Oroglas panels to fall out
OL,20,Fof their frames.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/13
