OL,3,CSummerland 50th Anniversary: What
OL,4,Chappened and why does it matter?
OL,6,FOnce alight, the roof burnt out in
OL,7,Faround 10 minutes, causing burning
OL,8,Fdebris to fall from the roof, burning
OL,9,Fpeople below.
OL,11,FThe report highlighted how quick
OL,12,FOroglas burned as a building material
OL,13,Fonce it had been heated by other
OL,14,Fmaterials built close to it.
OL,16,FIt also concluded that the high number
OL,17,Fof deaths were due to the delayed
OL,18,Fevacuation of the building and the
OL,19,Finadequate means of escape.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/13
