OL,3,CSummerland 50th Anniversary: What
OL,4,Chappened and why does it matter?
OL,6,FThe inquiry also found that no fire
OL,7,Falarm sounded when Summerland was
OL,8,Fengulfed in flames, leading to a major
OL,9,Fdelay in the evacuation.
OL,11,FThe SFC concluded the architects made
OL,12,Fa number of errors which led to the
OL,13,Ftragedy, but 'no villains' were
OL,14,Fsingled out.
OL,16,FIn the closing paragraph it states:
OL,17,F"In all the above inadequacies and
OL,18,Ffailings, it seems to the Commission
OL,19,Fthat there were no villains.
