OL,3,CSummerland 50th Anniversary: What
OL,4,Chappened and why does it matter?
OL,6,F"Within a certain climate of euphoria
OL,7,Fat the development of this interesting
OL,8,Fconcept, there were many human errors
OL,9,Fand failures and it was the
OL,10,Faccumulation of these, too much
OL,11,Freliance on an 'old boy' network and
OL,12,Fsome very ill-defined and poor
OL,13,Fcommunications which led to the
OL,14,Fdisaster."
OL,16,FNo criminal charges were ever brought,
OL,17,Fand a series of 34 recommendations
OL,18,Fwere made in relation to building
OL,19,Fregulations.
